page.title: 18JOANNE GASCOIGNE'S DAY
page.content: I wake up at 7.30 get dressed then go down stairs.At 8.00 I have breakfast then wait for the coach which comes at 8.20.When I arrive at school I go in and put out the overhead projector then I go and do 9-a-day(maths).At 9.00 we go into assembly then Mary Moakes and I put the hi-fi away.In class we do language work and at 10.30 we have play.Next it's environmental studies.At 12.00 we have dinner then play,then we come in and do P.E.At home time I get on the coach and when I get home I wait for mom. Then at 7.00 we have tea.After tea I do my homework, then I go to bed.
